Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早又戴着莫名其妙的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.71,0:01:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你别这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.92,0:01:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不这样就拿不出干劲来嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那干劲到底是用来干什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.50,0:02:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯先生  真壁司令来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.50,0:02:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.22,0:02:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  近藤剑司驾驶阿赫特号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.17,0:02:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯卫驾驶菲弗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的儿子跟女人跑了\N就让别人的儿子上法弗尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁司令不是那样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.10,0:02:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的女儿驾驶不了你才能这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.16,0:02:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我早有心理准备了却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克斯号和菲尔号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实只有德莱号的话就太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.69,0:02:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作为父亲  到现在究竟做过什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.45,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真耐人寻味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.45,0:02:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的性命就交给你和总士了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.79,0:02:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他活着还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.66,0:02:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.42,0:03:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子  近藤和小楯要驾驶法弗尼尔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.04,0:03:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又只有我什么也做不了  只能看着他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.85,0:03:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子以前也是这种心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.45,0:03:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每次给她看学校的照片时\N她也是这么寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.47,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今才了解翔子的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.74,0:03:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没法把一骑和皆城的事告诉她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12话  不在～焦急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要当驾驶员  真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说是已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司  如果你不愿意妈妈会替你说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.60,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了  这样就能钓马子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笨蛋儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.05,0:04:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  今天就休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天为了调整法弗尼尔也没睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是作为父亲不得不做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.92,0:04:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙  尽管吩咐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  吃饭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.74,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的人为什么能当诺顿模型的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.51,0:05:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗时心虚胆怯  还被我砍掉了手臂的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.68,0:05:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  那个红色家伙的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.49,0:05:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  那架机体就交给我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经用不着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.36,0:05:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为人类怎么能若无其事地战斗  一定是疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.26,0:05:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把我放出去  像你这样的小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.19,0:05:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门  部队的负责人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即把他叫来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对我  你知道有什么后果吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把门打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.72,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我是遵照命令做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.25,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  新国联有什么联络吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.15,0:06:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  别在途中撞上菲斯特姆就好了一骑他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.51,0:06:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把原稿存在磁盘13的文件夹里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.41,0:06:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在确认  马上就送到印刷部去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.02,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.58,0:06:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过最近那么忙  你还能画那么多页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了梦想而战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.26,0:06:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也写着同样的台词啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.93,0:06:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.06,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  给你一瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.55,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4时方向  距离785有重力反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.36,0:07:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标…以740方向朝岛屿靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.81,0:07:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所罗门判断完毕  断定为斯芬克司型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.88,0:07:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.54,0:07:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前的不一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔打开驾驶系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.78,0:07:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用运输机前往群岛进行狙击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.88,0:07:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有防卫系统的掩护吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  敌人现在和岛屿拉开了距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎和以前的进攻类型不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.04,0:07:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  在20秒内结束检测
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输机已经准备完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.98,0:07:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了登机后的检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.76,0:07:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.27,0:07:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  把孩子们平安无事地带回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.52,0:08:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去告诉卫那样不好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他说也没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.19,0:08:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那方面他相当顽固啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什么打扮  等等  卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.92,0:08:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是男人的首战  就让他这样去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.42,0:08:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三架法弗尼尔在运输机中准备完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将前往目的地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与敌人接触之前菲弗号先行降落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开驾驶系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士  我的行动代号是GOBAIN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔菲弗号  出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOBAIN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.93,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输机发射准备  完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两人还没经过变化测试就上战场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.71,0:09:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在连合作用的影响下\N能预计他们的精神状态会发生变化吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.24,0:09:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良在上次的出击中\N曾被相当强的攻击意识所支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.22,0:09:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计剩下的两人也会有所变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.65,0:09:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,航向确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意一下驾驶员的精神变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.85,0:09:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑就不会发生那样的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运输机准备发射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有2分钟将抵达目的群岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离运输机后4秒打开各系统  到预定地点待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接到命令前绝对不要出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪儿  它在哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Ray出现在前方20公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.91,0:10:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会遭到正面袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急脱离  发射运输舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.18,0:10:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一防护盾受袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.53,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是远距离进攻的类型吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了  妈妈  我想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的菲斯特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔着陆确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示各驾驶员状况数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.04,0:11:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员的精神状态果然有很大的变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.16,0:11:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经先下手为强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.34,0:11:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会根据情况  重新安排作战方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫  你要干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士  咲良  剑司  听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.30,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  等等菲弗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GOBAIN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我故意去引敌人攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良和剑司趁机打倒敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.44,0:11:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事真的能办到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.25,0:11:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能打倒敌人怎样都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让我战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.40,0:11:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  菲弗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.12,0:11:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你的防御装备  如果不能完全挡住敌人的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.26,0:11:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体都会陷入危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.00,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使胜机只有0%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会坚信着明日的朝阳而战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.52,0:11:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是机动武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是胡闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.86,0:12:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自作主张  全体脱离连接系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.09,0:12:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个战术还不错  让他们试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.21,0:12:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是精神变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.18,0:12:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该由咲良主攻的部分  现在由卫完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.38,0:12:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信他的防御装备可以发挥最佳效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人是远程直线攻击型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.45,0:12:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲弗号应该足以应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要相信驾驶员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.13,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.48,0:12:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标向法弗尼尔着陆地点移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.69,0:12:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一防护盾被突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔全体散开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.26,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在敌人进攻同时  阿赫特号从3时方向进行射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.55,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁此期间  德莱号绕到敌人后方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.92,0:13:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在  一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOBAIN SMASH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认敌人已被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有驾驶员平安无事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良  幸好你没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.40,0:14:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮  笨蛋儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.76,0:14:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在拼命战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.14,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公  卫他…卫他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.67,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了  卫他成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能平安无事真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.22,0:14:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在羽佐间老师面前  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我真的很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.38,0:14:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请代我好好鼓励卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一定要被关进这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.72,0:15:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们保护了岛屿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.66,0:15:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是独断行动的惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里清醒一下头脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.16,0:15:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实如总士所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫  你怎么还戴着那玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.72,0:15:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你的射击太差劲  总士才没有满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我反省一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  动作再利索点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.86,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我们为什么在这种地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  干嘛那么恐怖的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.29,0:15:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吓人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.24,0:15:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在连合作用的影响下  一时的精神变化会因人而异
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.36,0:15:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间和春日井也有那种迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.97,0:15:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没想到会有那么大变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.13,0:16:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次必须要让他们在精神变化之下出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.63,0:16:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  一骑为什么没有变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.01,0:16:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与法弗尼尔一体化的条件有\N遗传特质和积极的自我否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.95,0:16:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是后者对搭乘时的变化有很大影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.02,0:16:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一骑平时就一直对自己加以否定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以乘上法弗尼尔  内心也不会有什么变化吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以这么说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.27,0:16:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是对他来说  因为有你在身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身心才得以安定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望得到安定的是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑就是因为明白这一点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.97,0:16:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.86,0:16:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑为什么离开  你有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.08,0:16:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积极的自我否定的尽头  就是绝对的肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.57,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈愿你和一骑终有一日达到那一境界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话就好像一骑还在岛上似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为他还会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上前我会放那三人出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们的父母很想见他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.51,0:17:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.50,0:17:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是怀有敬意  与对方的距离就会拉得越远吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和过去的皆城一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.78,0:17:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那笨蛋儿子现在正被关在人类军的牢里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.99,0:17:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起驾驶法弗尼尔战斗  还是那样比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.19,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样想恐怕是没资格作指挥官吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.63,0:18:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.14,0:18:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑还是没来联络吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.00,0:18:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能遭到了菲斯特姆的袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者被新国联抓住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎样都与我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要那么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.68,0:18:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他没有理解自己？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.82,0:18:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有想过去理解一骑吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我理解他的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过齐格菲系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的感情  潜意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.58,0:18:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗时的思考都交流过好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.09,0:18:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过机械窥探人的内心  这样就能理解吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.02,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对一骑了解什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少比你了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.77,0:19:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我是个没用处的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在CDC也派不上什么大用场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.10,0:19:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能驾驶法弗尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.52,0:19:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此  看着大家拼命战斗还觉得羡慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.16,0:19:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.88,0:19:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.97,0:19:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.85,0:19:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在不需要战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.20,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.60,0:19:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城  为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.51,0:19:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有这样告诉一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.54,0:19:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能说的话  我早就说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了  真壁一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.21,0:20:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这房间那么小  对不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要呼吸一下外面的空气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.57,0:20:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道生先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  你第一次离岛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.05,0:20:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.15,0:20:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  不要怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.31,0:20:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.52,0:20:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就到摩尔多瓦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.83,0:20:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  道生先生现在住在哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有固定的住所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.35,0:20:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前父亲带我离岛之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.55,0:20:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直作为人类军的士兵四处征战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.77,0:20:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军的…士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我吗  龙宫岛的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  妈妈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.38,0:20:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 听说在菲斯特姆第一次出现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和仓麻一起被同化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应不应该告诉老爸呢  真头疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.21,0:21:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  那个…远见弓子现在怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.49,0:21:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子小姐  在学校是保健室的医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙当医生了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.72,0:21:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗  她以前的梦想是到东京当偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.39,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.56,0:21:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRIBBLE6号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.63,0:21:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRIBBLE6号？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的行动代号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  加侬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.58,0:21:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命时别叫那个硬生生的代号  叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.91,0:21:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的上司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对上司不能直呼其名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是脑筋不开窍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  这家伙是加侬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把你的法弗尼尔的手臂砍断的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.34,0:21:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  刚才已经谈过话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加侬会跟人谈话真是少见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.73,0:22:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看中一骑了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.79,0:22:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说这个  就快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.25,0:22:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.47,0:22:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新国联人类军的摩尔多瓦基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.47,0:23:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.83,0:23:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被腐蚀的现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.47,0:23:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与过去的牵绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.73,0:23:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而未来等待着的是  新的分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.35,0:23:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  苍穹的Fafnir  第十三话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.17,0:23:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲斯特姆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.47,0:23:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
